                        Click the summary button in the article sidebar.</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="tip-card">
                        <div class="tip-icon">‚å®Ô∏è</div>
                        <strong>Keyboard Shortcuts</strong>
                        <p><code>Ctrl+S</code> to save, <code>Ctrl+N</code> to create a new article. 
